<title>Endpoints</title>

<p>The <tag>endpoint</tag> tag is a point with an additional <attr>open</attr> attribute, which defaults to false.</p>


<graph>
  <endpoint name="A">(3,4)</endpoint>
  <endpoint name="B" open>(-3,5)</endpoint>
  <lineSegment endpoints="$A $B" />
</graph>

